---
title: "US30 — Access expert content / deliverables"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>ExpertDetailScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>RequestService
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>ServiceRequest · Deliverable
  A->>B: browse expert content / offerings
  B->>C: requestService(serviceId)
  C->>E: createServiceRequest(serviceId)
  note right of E: payment simulated —<br/>price fields only, no gateway
  E-->>C: ServiceRequest (created)
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (purchased)
  A->>B: open My Purchases
  B->>C: loadDeliverables(requestId)
  C->>E: listDeliverables(requestId)
  E-->>C: List (Deliverable)
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (content)
  B-->>A: content delivered via Deliverable
  note over E: planned — createServiceRequest / listDeliverables<br/>via SupabaseGateway (RLS)
